        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[【交流】关于开展“华园高水平留学计划”本科插班生专项申报工作的通知]]></title>
            <link>https://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/cms/article/view.do?type=posts&amp;id=eec18a7b9b43f62c019d1d8ab3840087</link>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">scut-jw-eec18a7b9b43f62c019d1d8ab3840087</guid>
            <pubDate>Tue, 24 Mar 2026 08:25:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<p><strong>类型:</strong> 交流 | <strong>日期:</strong> 2026.03.24 | <a href="https://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/cms/article/view.do?type=posts&id=eec18a7b9b43f62c019d1d8ab3840087">查看原文</a></p><hr><div class="content">



<p><span style="font-family: 微软雅黑;"></span></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">各学院</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">（系）</span><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">：</span></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style='text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-family: "Segoe UI"; font-size: 16px;'>为<span style="letter-spacing: 0px; color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-indent: 32px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);">助力学校“双一流”建设，</span></span><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; font-family: "Segoe UI";'><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: quote-cjk-patch, Inter, system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Segoe UI", Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, "Open Sans", "Helvetica Neue", sans-serif; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 20px; text-indent: 32px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);"></span>加大拔尖创新人才培养力度，现启动“华园高水平留学计划”本科插班生专项申报工作，支持优秀本科生赴世界一流高校开展学期或学年交流学习。</span>有关事项通知如下：</span></p><h4 style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">一</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">、申请条件</span></strong></h4><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><strong>（一）基本条件</strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">：</span></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">1. 拥护中国共产党的领导和中国特色社会主义制度，热爱祖国、品德良好、遵纪守法，具有服务国家、服务社会、服务人民的责任感和端正的世界观、人生观、价值观。</span></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">2. 具有良好专业基础和发展潜力，恪守学术道德、遵守学术规范，在工作、学习中表现突出，具有学成回国为国家建设服务的事业心和使命感。</span></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">3. <span style="font-family:Segoe UI">具有中华人民共和国国籍，不具有国外永久居留权。申请时年龄满18周岁。</span></span></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">4. 身体健康，心理健康。</span></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">5. 我校理工医类学科正式在籍全日制本科生。</span></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">6. 外语水平满足留学单位的学习要求。</span></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">7. <span style="font-family:Segoe UI">派出时间为即日起至</span>2026年8月31日（含）。</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><strong>（二）学业与项目要求</strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">：</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px">1. </span><strong>学业成绩</strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">：原则上必修课原始成绩百分制平均学分绩点（</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman';letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">GPA</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">）在本专业排名前</span><span style="font-family: 'Times New Roman';letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">50%</span><span style="letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">。</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px">2. </span><strong>项目</strong><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">要求</span></strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">：已获得学校组织的</span><strong>美国加州大学、英国爱丁堡大学、英国伯明翰大学、瑞典皇家理工学院</strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"><span style="font-family:sans-serif">等世界高水平大学的学期</span>/学年交流项目录取资格</span><span style="font-family: 宋体;letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">，</span><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>留学期限为</span><strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">3—12个月</span></strong><span style="letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">。</span></p><h4 style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">二</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">、资助内容</span></strong></h4><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">1. </span><strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>一次性往返国际旅费及签证费</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI">：实报实销，每人次最高不超过</span>1.5万元人民币（限经济舱）。</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">2. </span><strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>留学期间奖学金生活费</span></strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>：参照国家公派留学人员奖学金标准执行。</span></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">注</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">：在校期间，每位学生只能享受一次本项出国（境）交流资助。</span></p><h4 style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:8px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><strong><span style="font-family: 宋体;color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">三</span></strong><strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">、申请流程</span></strong></h4><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">1. </span><strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>个人申请</span></strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>：学生在完成项目申请并获得录取资格后，登录学校“</span><strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>门户—办事大厅—本科生院—本科生出国（境）学习交流资助申请</span></strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>”，按要求上传邀请函等材料，</span><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体;">于</span><strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">2026年7月1日</span></strong><strong><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体;">前</span></strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>提交资助申请。</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">2. </span><strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>学院初审</span></strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>：学院对申请人的道德品行、学业能力等进行综合考察。于</span><strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">2026年7月3日17:00前</span></strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>登录“门户-办事大厅”完成线上审核与推荐。</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-weight: bold;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">3. </span><strong><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体;">学校</span></strong><strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>评审</span></strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>：本科生院进行评审并确定拟资助名单，报国际交流与合作处备案。</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:28px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><strong><span style="color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: 宋体;">四、</span></strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>联系方式</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>本科生院</span></strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>：蒋老师</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>电话</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI">：</span>020-87110734</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><strong><span style='color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; font-size: 16px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-family: "Segoe UI";'>邮箱</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI">：</span>fwjiang@scut.edu.cn</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)">QQ咨询群</span></strong><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"><span style="font-family:Segoe UI">：</span>549245464</span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style='font-family: "Segoe UI"; color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px;'><br/></span></p><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style='font-family: "Segoe UI"; color: rgb(15, 17, 21); letter-spacing: 0px; background: rgb(255, 255, 255); font-size: 14px;'></span></p><h1 class="rich_media_title" id="activity-name" style='-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; font-size: 22px; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.9); line-height: 1.4; user-select: text; font-family: "PingFang SC", system-ui, -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, "Helvetica Neue", "Hiragino Sans GB", "Microsoft YaHei UI", "Microsoft YaHei", Arial, sans-serif; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-wrap: wrap; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);'>     <span style="font-size: 14px;">全文链接：</span><a href="https://mp.weixin.qq.com/s/UHgi4hlfCXPy2DCvwb7qng" style="text-decoration: underline; -webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: 14px;" target="_blank" title="华南理工大学“华园高水平留学计划”专项报名通知"><span style="-webkit-tap-highlight-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0); margin: 0px; padding: 0px; outline: 0px; white-space-collapse: preserve; font-size: 14px;">华南理工大学“华园高水平留学计划”专项报名通知</span></a></h1><p style="margin-top:0;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:0;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px;background: rgb(255, 255, 255)"></span><br/></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px"> </span></p><p style="margin-top:16px;margin-right:0;margin-bottom:16px;margin-left:0;text-indent:32px;text-autospace:ideograph-numeric;text-align:right;line-height:150%;background:rgb(255,255,255)"><span style="font-family: 'Segoe UI';color: rgb(15, 17, 21);letter-spacing: 0;font-size: 16px">本科生院<br/>2026年3月24日</span></p><p><br/></p>
