<p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#444444">各院（系）：</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#444444">根据《关于开展AI辅助课程认定工作的通知》要求，经课程负责人申请、专家组评审，拟予以通过认定课程</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif;color:#444444">26</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#444444">门，现将课程名单（见附件）予以公示，公示期为</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif;color:#444444">2026</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#444444">年</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif;color:#444444">3</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#444444">月</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif;color:#444444">18</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#444444">日</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif;color:#444444">-3</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#444444">月</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif;color:#444444">22</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#444444">日。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#444444">在公示期内，任何个人和单位如有异议，须实名向本科生院进行书面反映并提供具体事实依据，否则不予受理。</span></p><p style="text-indent:37px"><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:宋体;color:#444444">联系人：詹老师，联系电话：</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif;color:#444444">81182314</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family: 宋体;color:#444444">，邮箱：</span><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif;color:#444444">zhanhj@scut.edu.cn</span></p><p><span style="font-size:20px;font-family:'Helvetica',sans-serif;color:#444444"> </span></p><p><span style="font-size:19px;font-family:'微软雅黑',sans-serif;color:#444444"> </span></p><p style="line-height: 16px;">　　<a href="http://jw.scut.edu.cn/zhinan/static/upload/file/20260318/1773801457124037065.xlsx" style="font-size:12px; color:#0066cc;" title="附件：